</a></li> <li class="author"><a href="/cdsr/doi/10.1002/14651858.CD014719/information#CD014719-cr-0008">Jeremy N Rodrigues</a></li> <li class="author"><a href="/cdsr/doi/10.1002/14651858.CD014719/information#CD014719-cr-0009">Jonathan A Cook</a></li> <li class="author"><a href="/cdsr/doi/10.1002/14651858.CD014719/information#CD014719-cr-0010">Daniel Prieto-Alhambra</a></li> <li class="author"><a href="/cdsr/doi/10.1002/14651858.CD014719/information#CD014719-cr-0011">Mike J Clarke</a></li> <li class="author"><a href="/cdsr/doi/10.1002/14651858.CD014719/information#CD014719-cr-0012">Matthew L Costa</a></li> </ul> <span class="author declaration"> <a href="/cdsr/doi/10.1002/14651858.CD014719/information/en#CD014719-sec1-0007" class="declarationsOfInterestLink">Authors' declarations of interest</a> </span> </div> </div> </div> <div class="publication-metadata-block"> <p> <span class="publish-date">Version published: 21 June 2022 </span> <a href="/cdsr/doi/10.1002/14651858.CD014719/information/en#versionTable" class="whatsNewLink">Version history</a> </p> <div class="doi-header"> <a href="https://doi.org/10.1002/14651858.CD014719">https://doi.org/10.1002/14651858.CD014719</a> </div> </div> </header> <div class="publication-control-bar"> <span class="publication-control-button publication-control-collapse"> Collapse all </span> <span class="publication-control-button publication-control-expand"> Expand all </span> </div> <section class="abstract"> <div class="section-header section-collapse-header" id="CD014719-abs-0001" lang="en"> <h2 class="title section-collapse-title"> Abstract <i aria-hidden="true" class="fa fa-caret-up section-collapse-icon"></i> </h2> </div> <div class="abstract full_abstract" id="CD014719-abs-0001" lang="en"> <section id="CD014719-abs1-0001"> <h3 class="title" id="CD014719-abs1-0001">Objectives</h3> <p>This is a protocol for a Cochrane Review (intervention). The objectives are as follows:</p> <p>To compare the effects of antimicrobial sutures vers